




       Aug. 28. 1780
      



Mr. Adamss Compliments to Mr. Gridley, and desires to know whether there is in Print, either in English or French, any particular description of the islands of St. Johnthe two Miseres, the Isles [95]Perce Bonaventure and Magdalen, Miqulen and St. Peters, in short of all the Islands in and about he Gulph of St. Laurence? If there is what is the Title of the Book? What is the best Map extant of those Seas and Islands. If there is neither Book nor Map, will Mr. Gridley do Mr. Adams the favour to give him a <short> description in Writing as particular as Mr. Gridleys time will Admit?
